[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 6599,
        "end_time": 8543,
        "text": "What is bipolar disorder?"
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 8543,
        "end_time": 12605,
        "text": "The word bipolar means two extremes."
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 12605,
        "end_time": 16785,
        "text": "For the many millions experiencing\nbipolar disorder around the world,"
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 16785,
        "end_time": 20405,
        "text": "life is split between \ntwo different realities -"
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 20405,
        "end_time": 22836,
        "text": "elation and depression."
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 22836,
        "end_time": 25874,
        "text": "Although there are many variations\nof bipolar disorder,"
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 25874,
        "end_time": 27816,
        "text": "let&#39;s consider a couple."
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 27816,
        "end_time": 31915,
        "text": "Type 1 has extreme highs\nalongside the lows,"
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 31915,
        "end_time": 36506,
        "text": "while Type 2 involves briefer, \nless extreme periods of elation"
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 36506,
        "end_time": 39736,
        "text": "interspersed with long periods\nof depression."
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 39736,
        "end_time": 42545,
        "text": "For someone seesawing between\nemotional states,"
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 42545,
        "end_time": 48076,
        "text": "it can feel impossible to find the balance\nnecessary to lead a healthy life."
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 48076,
        "end_time": 52256,
        "text": "Type 1&#39;s extreme highs are known\nas manic episodes,"
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 52256,
        "end_time": 56775,
        "text": "and they can make a person range from\nfeeling irritable to invincible."
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 56775,
        "end_time": 61225,
        "text": "But these euphoric episodes exceed\nordinary feelings of joy,"
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 61225,
        "end_time": 63847,
        "text": "causing troubling symptoms \nlike racing thoughts,"
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 63847,
        "end_time": 65336,
        "text": "sleeplessness,"
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 65336,
        "end_time": 66516,
        "text": "rapid speech,"
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 66516,
        "end_time": 67962,
        "text": "impuslive actions,"
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 67962,
        "end_time": 70125,
        "text": "and risky behaviors."
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 70125,
        "end_time": 72904,
        "text": "Without treatment, these episodes\nbecome more frequent,"
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 72904,
        "end_time": 73827,
        "text": "intense,"
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 73827,
        "end_time": 76216,
        "text": "and take longer to subside."
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 76216,
        "end_time": 80626,
        "text": "The depressed phase of bipolar disorder\nmanifests in many ways -"
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 80626,
        "end_time": 81657,
        "text": "a low mood,"
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 81657,
        "end_time": 83719,
        "text": "dwindling interest in hobbies,"
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 83719,
        "end_time": 85257,
        "text": "changes in appetite,"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 85257,
        "end_time": 87857,
        "text": "feeling worthless or excessively guilty,"
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 87857,
        "end_time": 90147,
        "text": "sleeping either too much or too little,"
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 90147,
        "end_time": 92256,
        "text": "restlessness or slowness,"
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 92256,
        "end_time": 95562,
        "text": "or persistent thoughts of suicide."
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 95562,
        "end_time": 98397,
        "text": "Worldwide, about one \nto three percent of adults"
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 98397,
        "end_time": 103597,
        "text": "experience the broad range of symptoms\nthat indicate bipolar disorder."
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 103597,
        "end_time": 106967,
        "text": "Most of those people are functional,\ncontributing members of society,"
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 106967,
        "end_time": 109527,
        "text": "and their lives, choices, \nand relationships"
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 109527,
        "end_time": 112097,
        "text": "aren&#39;t defined by the disorder,"
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 112097,
        "end_time": 115697,
        "text": "but still, for many, the consequences\nare serious."
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 115697,
        "end_time": 119426,
        "text": "The illness can undermine educational\nand professional performance,"
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 119426,
        "end_time": 120578,
        "text": "relationships,"
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 120578,
        "end_time": 121909,
        "text": "financial security,"
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 121909,
        "end_time": 125297,
        "text": "and personal safety."
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 125297,
        "end_time": 128407,
        "text": "So what causes bipolar disorder?"
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 128407,
        "end_time": 132558,
        "text": "Researchers think a key player is \nthe brain&#39;s intricate wiring."
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 132558,
        "end_time": 135949,
        "text": "Healthy brains maintain strong connections\nbetween neurons"
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 135949,
        "end_time": 139488,
        "text": "thanks to the brain&#39;s continuous efforts\nto prune itself"
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 139488,
        "end_time": 144682,
        "text": "and remove unused or faulty\nneural connections."
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 144682,
        "end_time": 148977,
        "text": "This process is important because our \nneural pathways serve as a map"
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 148977,
        "end_time": 151389,
        "text": "for everything we do."
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 151389,
        "end_time": 153858,
        "text": "Using functional magnetic \nresonance imaging,"
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 153858,
        "end_time": 158099,
        "text": "scientists have discovered that the brain&#39;s \npruning ability is disrupted"
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 158099,
        "end_time": 160771,
        "text": "in people with bipolar disorder."
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 160771,
        "end_time": 163058,
        "text": "That means their neurons go haywire"
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 163058,
        "end_time": 166398,
        "text": "and create a network\nthat&#39;s impossible to navigate."
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 166398,
        "end_time": 169228,
        "text": "With only confusing signals as a guide,"
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 169228,
        "end_time": 173938,
        "text": "people with bipolar disorder develop\nabnormal thoughts and behaviors."
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 173938,
        "end_time": 175558,
        "text": "Also, psychotic symptoms,"
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 175558,
        "end_time": 177920,
        "text": "like disorganized speech and behavior,"
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 177920,
        "end_time": 179227,
        "text": "delusional thoughts,"
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 179227,
        "end_time": 180488,
        "text": "paranoia,"
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 180488,
        "end_time": 181786,
        "text": "and hallucinations"
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 181786,
        "end_time": 185959,
        "text": "can emerge during extreme phases\nof bipolar disorder."
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 185959,
        "end_time": 191379,
        "text": "This is attributed to the overabundance\nof a neurotransmitter called dopamine."
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 191379,
        "end_time": 197450,
        "text": "But despite these insights, we can&#39;t pin\nbipolar disorder down to a single cause."
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 197450,
        "end_time": 200069,
        "text": "In reality, it&#39;s a complex problem."
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 200069,
        "end_time": 203369,
        "text": "For example, the brain&#39;s amygdala\nis involved in thinking,"
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 203369,
        "end_time": 204780,
        "text": "long-term memory,"
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 204780,
        "end_time": 206831,
        "text": "and emotional processing."
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 206831,
        "end_time": 211419,
        "text": "In this brain region, factors as varied\nas genetics and social trauma"
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 211419,
        "end_time": 216609,
        "text": "may create abnormalities and trigger\nthe symptoms of bipolar disorder."
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 216609,
        "end_time": 218640,
        "text": "The condition tends to run in families,"
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 218640,
        "end_time": 222200,
        "text": "so we do know that genetics have\na lot to do with it."
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 222200,
        "end_time": 225469,
        "text": "But that doesn&#39;t mean there&#39;s\na single bipolar gene."
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 225469,
        "end_time": 228520,
        "text": "In fact, the likelihood of developing\nbipolar disorder"
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 228520,
        "end_time": 232009,
        "text": "is driven by the interactions between\nmany genes"
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 232009,
        "end_time": 235591,
        "text": "in a complicated recipe we&#39;re still\ntrying to understand."
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 235591,
        "end_time": 237120,
        "text": "The causes are complex,"
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 237120,
        "end_time": 242360,
        "text": "and consequently, diagnosing and living\nwith bipolar disorder is a challenge."
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 242360,
        "end_time": 245280,
        "text": "Despite this, the disorder \nis controllable."
    },
    {
        "index": 79,
        "start_time": 245280,
        "end_time": 249801,
        "text": "Certain medications like lithium can help\nmanage risky thoughts and behaviors"
    },
    {
        "index": 80,
        "start_time": 249801,
        "end_time": 251971,
        "text": "by stabilizing moods."
    },
    {
        "index": 81,
        "start_time": 251971,
        "end_time": 257861,
        "text": "These mood stabilizing medications work by\ndecreasing abnormal activity in the brain,"
    },
    {
        "index": 82,
        "start_time": 257861,
        "end_time": 261070,
        "text": "thereby strengthening the viable\nneural connections."
    },
    {
        "index": 83,
        "start_time": 261070,
        "end_time": 264451,
        "text": "Other frequently used medications\ninclude antipsychotics,"
    },
    {
        "index": 84,
        "start_time": 264451,
        "end_time": 267281,
        "text": "which alter the effects of dopamine,"
    },
    {
        "index": 85,
        "start_time": 267281,
        "end_time": 269472,
        "text": "and electroconvulsive therapy,"
    },
    {
        "index": 86,
        "start_time": 269472,
        "end_time": 272772,
        "text": "which works like a carefully controlled\nseizure in the brain,"
    },
    {
        "index": 87,
        "start_time": 272772,
        "end_time": 275752,
        "text": "is sometimes used as \nan emergency treatment."
    },
    {
        "index": 88,
        "start_time": 275752,
        "end_time": 278031,
        "text": "Some bipolar patients reject treatment"
    },
    {
        "index": 89,
        "start_time": 278031,
        "end_time": 280321,
        "text": "because they&#39;re afraid it will\ndim their emotions"
    },
    {
        "index": 90,
        "start_time": 280321,
        "end_time": 282451,
        "text": "and destroy their creativity."
    },
    {
        "index": 91,
        "start_time": 282451,
        "end_time": 286062,
        "text": "But modern psychiatry is actively\ntrying to avoid that."
    },
    {
        "index": 92,
        "start_time": 286062,
        "end_time": 289753,
        "text": "Today, doctors work with patients\non a case-by-case basis"
    },
    {
        "index": 93,
        "start_time": 289753,
        "end_time": 293351,
        "text": "to administer a combination of treatments\nand therapies"
    },
    {
        "index": 94,
        "start_time": 293351,
        "end_time": 296973,
        "text": "that allows them to live \nto their fullest possible potential."
    },
    {
        "index": 95,
        "start_time": 296973,
        "end_time": 300182,
        "text": "And beyond treatment, people with\nbipolar disorder can benefit"
    },
    {
        "index": 96,
        "start_time": 300182,
        "end_time": 302312,
        "text": "from even simpler changes."
    },
    {
        "index": 97,
        "start_time": 302312,
        "end_time": 304091,
        "text": "Those include regular exercise,"
    },
    {
        "index": 98,
        "start_time": 304091,
        "end_time": 305462,
        "text": "good sleep habits,"
    },
    {
        "index": 99,
        "start_time": 305462,
        "end_time": 308023,
        "text": "and sobriety from drugs and alcohol,"
    },
    {
        "index": 100,
        "start_time": 308023,
        "end_time": 312412,
        "text": "not to mention the acceptance\nand empathy of family and friends."
    },
    {
        "index": 101,
        "start_time": 312412,
        "end_time": 315522,
        "text": "Remember, bipolar disorder \nis a medical condition,"
    },
    {
        "index": 102,
        "start_time": 315522,
        "end_time": 317340,
        "text": "not a person&#39;s fault,"
    },
    {
        "index": 103,
        "start_time": 317340,
        "end_time": 318992,
        "text": "or their whole identity,"
    },
    {
        "index": 104,
        "start_time": 318992,
        "end_time": 320969,
        "text": "and it&#39;s something that can be controlled"
    },
    {
        "index": 105,
        "start_time": 320969,
        "end_time": 324489,
        "text": "through a combination of medical \ntreatments doing their work internally,"
    },
    {
        "index": 106,
        "start_time": 324489,
        "end_time": 329019,
        "text": "friends and family fostering acceptance\nand understanding on the outside,"
    },
    {
        "index": 107,
        "start_time": 329019,
        "end_time": 332464,
        "text": "and people with bipolar disorder \nempowering themselves"
    },
    {
        "index": 108,
        "start_time": 332464,
        "end_time": 334584,
        "text": "to find balance in their lives."
    }
]